data.description: Lots of great space indoors and out in this home and even more room to expand in the basement. The inside is mostly comprised of real hard wood floors throughout and is adorned throughout with wood details on ceilings and walls. The Master Bedroom is a huge space to retreat for the night complete with a spacious walk-in closet.  The heating and cooling system is an efficient mini split system powered by electricity. It's very safe and efficient. If gardening and/or the idea of being more self-sufficient appeals to you, this home has you covered. The backyard has a chicken coop complete with raised garden beds and a sunroom/greenhouse attached to the home. There is a large, fenced area setup perfectly for your family pets. Come and see what this great home has to offer!
